{% layout 'theme' %}

<style>
  .hh-page { background:#080808; color:#f2ede1; font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; min-height:60vh; }
  .hh-page-inner { max-width:780px; margin:0 auto; padding:80px 48px; }
  .hh-page h1 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:42px; font-weight:400; color:#f2ede1; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .hh-page-rule { width:48px; height:1px; background:#C4A843; margin-bottom:48px; }
  .hh-page h2 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:400; color:#f2ede1; margin:40px 0 16px; }
  .hh-page p { font-size:13px; color:rgba(242,237,225,0.55); line-height:1.9; font-weight:300; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .hh-page ol { padding-left:20px; }
  .hh-page ol li { font-size:13px; color:rgba(242,237,225,0.55); line-height:1.9; font-weight:300; margin-bottom:10px; }
  @media(max-width:768px){ .hh-page-inner{ padding:56px 24px; } .hh-page h1{ font-size:32px; } }
</style>

<div class="hh-page">
  <div class="hh-page-inner">
    <h1>Returns &amp; Exchanges</h1>
    <div class="hh-page-rule"></div>

    <p>We stand behind every piece we make. If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, we are here to help.</p>

    <h2>Return Policy</h2>
    <p>We accept returns within <strong style="color:#f2ede1;">60 days</strong> of the delivery date. Items must be unworn, undamaged, and in their original packaging. Sale items, personalized pieces, and final sale items are not eligible for return.</p>

    <h2>How To Start a Return</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Visit our Contact page and select "Return Request" as the subject.</li>
      <li>Include your order number and the reason for your return.</li>
      <li>Our team will respond within 1&ndash;2 business days with a prepaid return label and instructions.</li>
      <li>Pack your item securely and drop it off at any authorized carrier location.</li>
      <li>Once we receive and inspect your return, a refund will be issued to your original payment method within 5&ndash;7 business days.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Exchanges</h2>
    <p>We do not process direct exchanges. To exchange an item, please return the original piece following the steps above and place a new order for the replacement item.</p>

    <h2>Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
    <p>If your item arrived damaged or defective, please contact us within 7 days of delivery. Include photos of the damage and your order number, and we will arrange a replacement or full refund at no cost to you.</p>
  </div>
</div>
